义乌“另类”劝返：疫情期不返回就发钱 有社区房东主动减免房租。
Yiwu "alternative" persuasion: do not return to the epidemic period to send money to community landlords active rent relief.
高飞昌2020-02-01 15:46。
Gao Feichang 2020-02-01 15: 46.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
文中图片来源：受访者提供。
Source of picture: Respondent provided.
经济观察网 记者 高飞昌 就在很多人为返京后能不能正常入住小区或村子而发愁时，1月31日，家住浙江义乌的刘先生在微信朋友圈分享了一个手机短信截图，足以让很多人“羡慕”。
On January 31, Mr. Liu, who lives in Yiwu, Zhejiang Province, shared a text-messaging screenshot of his mobile phone with friends around Weixin, enough to make many people "envy" him.
。
.
该条短信截图的文字内容显示如下。
The text of this text capture is shown below.
发信者：之前和你电话联系，你已同意疫情期间不回义乌，请你信守承诺，疫情结束后回来，收到后请回（疫情结束回义乌）可凭短信内回复记录带上身份证到四季社区领取500元的补助。
The sender: You have agreed not to return to Yiwu during the epidemic. Please keep your promise and come back when the outbreak is over. Please come back when you receive it.
收信者：疫情结束回义乌。
Recipient: The outbreak ended in Yiwu.
。
.
义乌劝外来人员缓返手机短信。
Yiwu urged foreigners to stay their mobile phone text messages.
据刘先生介绍，这是义乌市相关社区的工作人员发给该社区外地租户的短信，“内容属实，是义乌市政府带领下，各方面共同商讨决定的”。
According to Mr. Liu, this is a text message sent to the community by the staff of the relevant community in Yiwu. "It is true, it was decided by all parties under the leadership of the municipal government of Yiwu.
经济观察网记者为进一步了解信息，查询了当地的相关网站，发现义乌市在新冠肺炎疫情防控方面确有很多举措，给外来人员发放补助只是其中一个措施。
In order to learn more about the news, the reporter looked up the relevant local website, found that Yiwu city in the New Crown Pneumonia prevention and control do have a lot of initiatives, the granting of subsidies to outsiders is only one of the measures.
。
.
浙江当地媒体“浙江新闻”2月1日发布的新闻原文中显示：“在义乌市委市政府积极引导下，企业、群众纷纷支持响应，发动各种关系劝导疫区及重点地区人员延缓来义，对企业劝导成功按每人每月补贴500元。
"Under the active guidance of the municipal government of the city of Yiwu, enterprises and the masses have supported the response, mobilizing all kinds of relations to persuade people in epidemic areas and key areas to delay the epidemic, and subsidizing enterprises with a monthly subsidy of 500 yuan per person for success," Zhejiang News said
”。
"
记者还发现，1月31日，有一个非官方的“倡议书”在义乌当地民众的微信圈中流传，其中显示“抗击肺炎，我们重义轻利，不丢义乌人的脸面，在疫情没有结束之前，愿意给予房租减免！”，倡议人是义乌市稠江街道11个村民委员会。
An unofficial petition circulated among local people in Yiwu on Jan. 31 shows that "in the fight against pneumonia, we should pay more attention to justice and not lose the face of the Yiwu people, and be willing to grant rent relief before the epidemic is over," the spokesman said.
该文件附有这些倡议人的红色盖章。
The document was accompanied by the initiators' red seals.
。
.
义乌社区房东免租金倡议书。
Rent Free Initiative for Landlords of Yiwu Community.
据了解，浙江省义乌市是全国知名的“小商品之都”，具有外来人口众多、流动性强的特点，面对疫情和春节返程高峰的叠加因素，当地疫情防控形势严峻。
It is understood that Yiwu, Zhejiang Province, is a well-known "small commodity capital", with a large foreign population, high mobility, the face of the epidemic and the Spring Festival return peak factors, local epidemic prevention and control situation is serious.
对此义乌市加大了对外来人员的排查和登记，据当地近来的摸排统计，仅湖北籍流动人口登记数就有54900人。
The city of Yiwu has increased its efforts to check and register migrant workers, with 54,900 migrants registered in Hubei province alone, according to a recent mapping exercise.
针对外来人员，义乌实施了包括隔离、劝返、发补贴、免租等在内的多重防控措施。
In the case of outsiders, Yiwu has implemented multiple control measures, including isolation, persuasion, subsidies and rent-free access.
。
.
这些措施都是在义乌市政府的强力防控布局下全面展开的。
All these measures are carried out under the strong control arrangement of Yiwu city government.
经济观察网记者从义乌市人民政府官方网站看到，该市针对疫情已经连发9道“冠状病毒肺炎”防控指挥部令，涉及方方面面，包括公共交通停运、各类封闭场所关闭、保障物资供应、复工时间延长等等。
The official website of the Yiwu Municipal People's Government shows that the city has issued nine command orders for the prevention and control of coronavirus pneumonia, covering a wide range of issues, including the suspension of public transportation, the closure of various closed areas, the supply of supplies, and the extension of working hours.
。
.
实际上，全国范围内有很多大中城市都面临外来人口返程与疫情防控双重压力，但是在针对外来人员返程问题上的应对措施不一。
In fact, many large and medium-sized cities across the country face the dual pressure of return migration and disease prevention and control.
据经济观察网此前的报道，目前在北京，有多个社区出现拒绝外地返京人员入住、导致返京人员无处居住的现象，目前还没有完美的解决方案。
According to previous reports by the Economic Watch Network, there are no perfect solutions to the problem in several communities in Beijing, where people who have returned to Beijing have been denied entry, leading to no place to live.
1月31日，北京市政府发文指出，必需行业以外的企业2月9日24时前灵活安排工作。
On January 31, the Beijing municipal government issued a note saying companies outside essential industries had flexible schedules before 2400 hours on February 9.
。
.
而浙江、上海、广东等地更早时候就发布了各企业延迟至2月9日复工的决定，且不少地方有对商户、对外来人员免租的政策。
Zhejiang, Shanghai, Guangdong and other places earlier issued the decision to delay the resumption of work until February 9, and many places have a policy of free rent for merchants and outsiders.
截稿前，记者又看到，2月1日，浙江中国小商品城集团股份有限公司发布了针对集团所属市场商位使用权人的通知，提到原定开市时间2月5日，初定推迟到2月21日，推迟16天，且推迟期间商位使用费、物业费免费。
Before the deadline, the reporter saw that on February 1, Zhejiang China Commodity City Group Co., Ltd. issued a notice against the group of market users, mentioned that the original opening date of February 5, the initial postponed to February 21, 16 days, and deferred during the period of royalty, property fees free.
。
.
义乌小商品城免租通知本文经「原本」原创认证，作者经济观察报，访问yuanben.io查询【23YEG85U】获取授权信息。
Notice of rent-free access to Yiwu Commodity City This article has been "original" original certification, the author of the Economic Observer, visit yuanben.io query [23YEG85U] for authorization information.
。
.
